sentence.text: Mutations in Vps33 isoforms cause pigment dilution in mice (Vps33a, buff) and Drosophila (heterophilic cell-cell adhesion via plasma membrane cell adhesion molecules) and the neurogenic arthrogryposis, renal dysfunction and cholestasis syndrome in humans (mRNA splice site selection1, VPS33B).
